---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Aurora — Why Aurora" description="Calculation vs Interpretation.">
  <div class="page-container">
    <section class="subpage-hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">DIFFERENTIATION</span>
      <h1>Why Aurora</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">The transition from human interpretation to architectural calculation.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="comparison-section">
      <div class="comparison-grid">
        <div class="comparison-column">
          <h3>The Legacy Standard</h3>
          <p>Data dashboards that show what happened after it happened.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Retrospective analysis</li>
            <li>Subjective interpretation</li>
            <li>Latent response</li>
            <li>Absorbed errors</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-column active">
          <h3>The Aurora Standard</h3>
          <p>Calculation engines that show the structure of what is about to happen.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Predictive structural mapping</li>
            <li>Objective calculation</li>
            <li>Instantaneous response</li>
            <li>Eliminated exposure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="narrative-blocks">
      <div class="narrative-block">
        <h3>What Aurora Connects</h3>
        <p>Aurora bridges the gap between raw environmental data and strategic execution. It doesn't just collect information; it identifies the structural threads that connect market behavior, internal resources, and future risk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="narrative-block">
        <h3>What Aurora Reveals</h3>
        <p>Most organizations operate based on perceived trends. Aurora reveals the underlying mechanics of those trends, exposing the vulnerabilities and opportunities that are invisible to the naked eye—and to traditional analytics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="narrative-block">
        <h3>What Teams Usually Miss</h3>
        <p>Teams miss the "Closure Radio"—the point at which a decision becomes irreversible and its consequences become locked in. Aurora calculates this point in real-time, allowing for moves that preserve optionality.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-cta">
      <a href="/demo" class="cta-button">→ Put a move under calculation</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 24px 120px;
  }
  .subpage-hero {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 56px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 20px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .comparison-section {
    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }
  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .comparison-column {
    padding: 40px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .comparison-column.active {
    border-color: rgba(46, 91, 255, 0.3);
    background: rgba(46, 91, 255, 0.03);
  }
  .comparison-column h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .comparison-column p {
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .comparison-column ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .comparison-column li {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .comparison-column li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }
  .comparison-column.active li::before {
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }
  .narrative-blocks {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .narrative-block h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .narrative-block p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .page-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 40px;
  }
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
